kpi.name: M5012C3

kpi_info.title: NUMBER OF AVAILABLE HSUPA SUBUNITS IN FSM
kpi_info.use: "The number of the available subunits for HSUPA processing in the FSM. The counter indicates the minimum value of HW capacity and licensed capacity available for HSUPA in the FSM. The licensed capacity considered in this counter is the sum of HSUPA resource steps which can be allocated for HSUPA processing due to HSUPA Processing Set licenses allocated to schedulers of the FSM. UPDATED: The counter is updated when FSM configuration, HW capacity or licensed capacity is changed."

kpi.kpi_alias: NUMBER OF AVAILABLE HSUPA SUBUNITS IN FSM
